title: DO IT

description.plain:
“DO IT” marks the seventh track from Vultures 1, featuring Compton-born rapper YG and the late Californian rapper Nipsey Hussle.

The track samples Juvenile’s 1998 song “Back That Azz Up.” The posthumous intro from Nipsey Hussle comes from an unreleased song called “I Just Wanna Know” featuring Cardi B and Ty Dolla $ign.

The track was first previewed during the Las Vegas Vultures Rave on December 15, 2023. The song was then previewed at the Chicago and New York VULTURES Listening Experiences in February 2024.
